;font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; use_custom_fonts_primary_title=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_hover_title=&#8221;true&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bilancio positivo per il Gruppo, trainato dalle risorse del settore agroalimentare.<br \/>\nCon prospettive di crescita che guardano al futuro.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/marcellogabanaholding.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bresciaoggi-28.08.2020.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6600 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/marcellogabanaholding.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bresciaoggi-28.08.2020-272x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"272\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marcellogabanaholding.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bresciaoggi-28.08.2020-272x300.jpg 272w, https:\/\/marcellogabanaholding.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bresciaoggi-28.08.2020-330x364.jpg 330w, https:\/\/marcellogabanaholding.it\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bresciaoggi-28.08.2020.jpg 441w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 272px) 100vw, 272px\" \/><\/a>[\/vc_hoverbox]<div class=\"naix-empty-space \"><div class=\"nx_empty_space_lg\"  style=\"height: 20px\"><\/div><div class=\"nx_empty_space_md\"  style=\"height: 20px\"><\/div><div class=\"nx_empty_space_xs\"  style=\"height: 20px\"><\/div><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row_content&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_hoverbox image=&#8221;6753&#8243; primary_title=&#8221;Un 2020 chiuso con una prospettiva di crescita&#8221; primary_title_font_container=&#8221;font_size:25&#8243; primary_title_google_fonts=&#8221;font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal&#8221; hover_title=&#8221;&#8221; hover_title_google_fonts=&#8221;font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; use_cust